<p><b>Urgent appeal  
</b></p>
<p><b> 
</b></p>
<p>206. On <b>5 July 2007</b>, the Special Rapporteur on violence against women, its causes 
</p>
<p>and consequences, jointly with the Special Rapporteur on the promotion and 
</p>
<p>protection of the right to freedom of opinion and expression, the Special Rapporteur 
</p>
