</p>
<p>the Government regarding Ms. R. S.. Ms. R. S. is a campaigner for women&#8217;s rights 
</p>
<p>and a member of the One Million Signatures campaign, which calls for an end to 
</p>
<p>discriminatory laws against women in Iran. 
</p>
<p> 
</p>
<p>211. According to information received, on 8 October 2007, Ms. R. S. participated in 
</p>
<p>an event to mark the International Day of the Child during which she collected 
</p>
<p>signatures for the One Million Signatures campaign.  
</p>
<p> 
</p>
