</p>
<p>communication of 20 November 2006. The Special Rapporteur regrets that the 
</p>
<p>Government of Iran did not reply to her communication sent on 2 March 2007 and 
</p>
<p>reiterates her interest in receiving response from the Government in regard to the 
</p>
<p>allegation submitted and would be particularly interested to know whether these cases 
</p>
<p>have resulted in any arrests and prosecutions of alleged perpetrators.  
</p>
